metadata.name: David Lynch
metadata.description:
This a portrait of world famous director David Lynch, creator of "Twin Peaks", "Mulholland Drive" and many other amazing movies.

He is a big fan of smoking, so when he asked me:
- What I have to do in your frame?

I jus told him:
- Chill and smoke, Sir, and imagine your favorite movie on the screen.

I shot this portrait in the cinema, usind the additional LED-light with softbox and Sony A7R III camera.
